pr_title: [GSoC] Add Quick actions functionality and Image Crop Functionality
pr_body:
**What kind of change does this PR introduce?**
Added quick action functionality to navigate from the app icon. Added functionality to crop images.

**Issue Number:**

Fixes #974
Fixes #973 


**Did you add tests for your changes?**
No

**Snapshots/Videos:**

https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/57677520/130345376-f3a39fb3-9b70-4142-9696-f3e558e701d7.mp4


https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/57677520/130345481-afd06d29-4d34-4b42-b8f6-0d3f8bd8cacd.mp4


<!--Add snapshots or videos wherever possible.-->

**If relevant, did you update the documentation?**
Not Required

**Summary**

- Added Quick Actions functionality
- Added image crop functionality in image picker service
- Added Placeholder images 


**Does this PR introduce a breaking change?**
No

**Have you read the [contributing guide](https://github.com/PalisadoesFoundation/talawa/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md)?**
Yes
